---
// No necesita props
---

<div
  class="hero relative min-h-[200px] md:min-h-[400px] lg:min-h-[600px] flex items-center px-6 md:px-12 py-10 md:py-8 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-[#e0f6f6] to-[#4fafb1]"
>
  <!-- Texto superpuesto -->
  <div
    class="relative z-10 w-full mx-auto lg:max-w-7xl pl-0 md:pl-2 ml-1 md:ml-2"
  >
    <!-- Título principal -->
    <h1
      class="font-bold leading-[0.95] tracking-tight mb-1 md:mb-2 overflow-visible"
    >
      <span
        class="font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-[#2c9b9b] via-[#a1eaec] to-[#c0e6e6] bg-clip-text text-transparent text-[2.5rem] md:text-[3.5rem] lg:text-[4rem] xl:text-[4.5rem] block leading-[1.0]"
      >
        Un legado salesiano:<br />
        educación que transforma vidas
      </span>
    </h1>

    <!-- Subtítulo + Botón -->
    <div
      class="text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl text-[#2c9b9b] space-y-1 font-medium mb-10 mt-10"
    >
      <p>Formamos personas</p>
      <p>Íntegras y comprometidas.</p>
      <p>¿Listo para ser parte de nuestra misión?</p>

      <!-- Botón con flecha → -->
      <a
        href="#"
        class="inline-block mt-6 ml-4 md:ml-20 lg:ml-40 bg-[#2c9b9b] hover:bg-[#136d6d] text-white text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 group"
      >
        Admisión 2025
        <span
          class="inline-block ml-2 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1"
          >→</span
        >
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Imagen de fondo/superpuesta -->
  <div
  class="absolute right-0 top-10 w-full lg:w-1/2 z-0 flex items-center justify-center opacity-100"
>
  <img
    src="/images/santos.png"
    alt="Educación Salesiana"
    class="h-full max-h-[80vh] object-contain object-right rounded-[10%/10%]"
    style="
      -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 60%, transparent 100%);
      mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 60%, transparent 100%);
      -webkit-mask-repeat: no-repeat;
      mask-repeat: no-repeat;
      -webkit-mask-size: 100% 100%;
      mask-size: 100% 100%;
    "
  />
</div>
</div>
